# 🚀 Meta Ads Reporting & Spy Tool — Beta Requirements

Balanced MVP (Monitoring 70% | Spy 30%)

---

# 🛡 PART 1 — Ad Monitoring (Core Value)

---

## 1️⃣ Authentication

### Providers:
- Google OAuth
- Facebook OAuth (required for Meta Ads access)

### Requirements:

- Users can sign up / log in via:
  - Google
  - Facebook

- Facebook login must request:
  - ads_read permission
  - business_management (if required for account listing)

- Store:
  - provider
  - provider_user_id
  - email

---

## 2️⃣ Meta Account Connection

After Facebook login:

User must:

- Select Ad Account
- Grant access
- Store:
  - ad_account_id
  - encrypted_access_token
  - token_expiry

Implement:

- Token refresh logic
- Automatic refresh before expiry
- Error handling if token invalid

---

## 3️⃣ Metrics Pulling

Pull ONLY:

- Spend
- Impressions
- Clicks
- CTR
- CPC
- Frequency
- ROAS

Granularity:

- Daily level
- Store snapshot per day
- Do NOT recalculate live

Database tables:

User
MetaAccount
AdAccount
AdMetrics (daily)

---

## 4️⃣ Creative Health Monitor (Rule-Based)

Create:

analyzeAdHealth(last_7_days_data)

Return:

status:
- HEALTHY
- DECLINING
- FATIGUED

Rules:

- CTR drops > 20% over 3 days
- CPC increases > 25%
- Frequency > 3
- ROAS declining 3 consecutive days

Rules must be configurable via ENV variables.

Dashboard must show:

🟢 Healthy
🟡 Declining
🔴 Fatigued

Include tooltip explanation.

---

## 5️⃣ Email Alerts

Trigger when:

- Status changes from HEALTHY → DECLINING/FATIGUED

Send:

- Ad name
- Triggered rule
- Suggested manual review

Must use queue system (no blocking API route).

---

## 6️⃣ Weekly AI Summary

Runs:

- Once per week per ad account

Input to AI:

{
  biggest_metric_change,
  top_performing_ad,
  worst_performing_ad,
  trend_summary
}

AI must return:

{
  summary: string,
  suggested_action: string
}

Limit:
- Max 300 tokens

Store summary in DB.
Do not regenerate unless manually triggered.

---

# ⚔ PART 2 — AdSpy (Lightweight Support)

---

## 7️⃣ Meta Ad Library Search

Features:

- Keyword search
- Country filter
- Page filter
- Pagination

Store minimal fields:

SpyAd:
- ad_id
- page_name
- ad_copy
- creative_url
- country
- first_seen
- last_seen

Do NOT:
- Estimate impressions
- Scrape aggressively
- Run background crawling

Search must be user-triggered.

---

## 8️⃣ Inspiration Board

Users can:

- Save SpyAd
- Add client label
- Add tag
- Add note

Simple CRUD operations.

Must enforce:
- Ownership validation
- Tag filtering

---

## 9️⃣ AI Creative Tagging

Triggered manually via "Analyze".

Send to AI:

- ad_copy
- creative_url (optional)

AI must return:

{
  hook_type,
  emotional_trigger,
  creative_format,
  short_explanation
}

Strict schema validation required.
Cache result.
Do not auto-reanalyze.

---

# 🔐 Security Requirements

- Encrypt all Meta tokens
- Enforce Row Level Security in Supabase
- Rate limit AI endpoint
- Rate limit AdSpy search
- Validate ownership on all reads

---

# 🧪 Testing Requirements

Each module must have:

- Unit tests
- Integration tests
- Mocked external services

Minimum coverage: 80%

No module considered complete without passing tests.

---

# 🧠 Development Order (Mandatory)

1. Auth
2. Meta connection
3. Metrics pull + storage
4. Health engine
5. Dashboard UI
6. Email alerts
7. Weekly AI summary
8. Ad library search
9. Inspiration board
10. AI creative tagging

No skipping.
No parallel feature building.

---

# ❌ Out of Scope (Beta)

- Predictive modeling
- Impression estimation
- Budget optimization
- Auto ad suggestions
- Campaign editing
- Multi-platform integration
- Heavy analytics

---

This MVP must stay lean, deterministic, and stable.
